<br>
I have not done any scientific study of my question so . . .<br>
<br>
It just seems that for some reason when I use Temperance vs the Symbol, hp and Bulwark I take less damage in a solo fight.<br>
<br>
Like I said - haven't done any plotting of it. Could it be that mobs aggro differently? (sure damn hope not!!) But I seem to lose my health much more - cast HoT twice or even three times versus once.<br>
<br>
Has anyone else encountered this?<br>
